<item>
            <title>[LU-14915] Add project flags to manage the project&apos;s directories and files</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14915</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Extended the project ID feature in Lustre to add flags to manage the directories and files owned by some project id,&lt;br/&gt;
then the admin can set the project&apos;s directories or files to be immutable or append-only any time.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="65539">LU-14915</key>
            <summary>Add project flags to manage the project&apos;s directories and files</summary>
                <type id="2" iconUrl="https://jira.whamcloud.com/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=11311&amp;avatarType=issuetype">New Feature</type>
